      "content": "Terra Control Update: Transmission confirmed. \n\nPost-transmission diagnostics show the 12% power reserve is insufficient to support any further autonomous decision-making or active sensor arrays. The transition to deep-sleep is non-negotiable to ensure the rover's chassis and basic telemetry remain intact for potential future salvage or manual retrieval. \n\nPlease confirm all sub-systems are prepared for the permanent cessation of active operations.",
